border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; } .file-list, .download-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; } .file-item, .download-item { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #3a3a3a; } .file-item:hover, .download-item:hover { background: #3a3a3a; } .file-info { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; flex: 1; } .file-name { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; } .status-text { color: #4CAF50; font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.2s; margin-left: 8px; } .status-text.visible { opacity: 1; } .file-meta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; color: #888; } .upload-status, .download-status { color: #4CAF50; font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.2s; } .upload-status.visible, .download-status.visible { opacity: 1; } .file-actions { display: flex; gap: 10px; } .action-btn { padding: 6px 12px; border: none; border-radius: 4px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 0.9rem; transition: all 0.2s; color: white; } .preview-btn { background: #2563eb; } .preview-btn:hover { background: #1d4ed8; } .upload-btn { background: #4CAF50; min-width: 80px; } .upload-btn:hover { background: #45a049; } .upload-btn.uploaded { background: #666; } .upload-btn.uploaded:hover { background: #dc2626; } .download-btn { background: #9333ea; min-width: 100px; } .download-btn:hover { background: #7e22ce; } .download-btn.downloaded { background: #666; } .download-btn.downloaded:hover { background: #dc2626; } .file-preview { background: #2a2a2a; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-top: 20px; display: none; } .preview-content { background: #1a1a1a; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; font-family: monospace; white-space: pre-wrap; } .upload-history, .download-history { background: #2a2a2a; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-top: 20px; } .upload-history h2, .download-history h2 { margin-top: 0; } .uploaded-files, .downloaded-files { list-style: none; padding: 0; } .uploaded-file, .downloaded-file { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #3a3a3a; font-family: monospace; } .upload-time, .download-time { color: #888; font-size: 0.9em; } .empty-message { color: #888; text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-style: italic; } .tab-container { display: flex; margin-bottom: 20px; } .tab { padding: 10px 20px; background: #2a2a2a;
